    "notes": "100kg Outsider, extraplanar flyer, #App: 1, Treasure: None. Claws (3d6), maw (3d6); armor 5; flies 20m/action; Morale +1. The dybbuk is only one rank below a fiend - a captain of hell! Immune to all weapons except for magical or silvered weapons. Immune to poison and disease. Knows 1d6 spells. In addition to using them itself, it may also teach them to its mortal allies or summoners. Enjoys an Advantage to resist hostile magic. The Dybbuk possesses three special abilities, per the Demonic Powers table.",
